OL,3,CLandlord says pubs are in 'survival
OL,4,Cmode' as business rate relief is cut
OL,6,FThe discount for retail, leisure and
OL,7,Fhospitality firms is set to be cut
OL,8,Ffrom 75% to 40% in the Welsh
OL,9,FGovernment's budget, which is due to
OL,10,Fbe published next week.
OL,12,FThe rate relief for premises in
OL,13,FEngland will remain at 75%.
OL,15,FThe British Beer and Pub Association
OL,16,Fsays the cut will cost Welsh pubs #3m
OL,17,Fa year.
